        {
            "title": "日股升23點收市　結束3日跌勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股反覆靠穩，全日升幅有限。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日經指數收報42633點，升23點，結束3日跌勢。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">指數本周累計跌1.7%，扭轉前兩星期升勢。</p>\n</div>",
